---
title: Spiced White Fish & Veggie Israeli Couscous with Honey Baby Carrots & Chargrilled Capsicum Mayo
description: Fish is one of those dinnertime dishes that demands attention, so set the mood with a fluffy couscous, sweet baby rainbow carrots and the fancy plates. Fall into a five-star atmosphere with chargrilled capsicum relish served with your fish, it’s worth it.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
